query:
-- Update Free plan
UPDATE plans SET 
  maxKeys = 10,
  maxFolders = 2,
  maxTeamMembers = 1,
  hasBackup = FALSE,
  has2FA = FALSE,
  hasAPI = FALSE,
  hasAlerts = FALSE,
  hasDashboard = FALSE,
  hasAudit = FALSE
WHERE name = 'Free';

-- Update Basic plan
UPDATE plans SET 
  maxKeys = 100,
  maxFolders = 10,
  maxTeamMembers = 1,
  price = 9.00,
  hasBackup = TRUE,
  has2FA = TRUE,
  hasAPI = FALSE,
  hasAlerts = FALSE,
  hasDashboard = FALSE,
  hasAudit = FALSE
WHERE name = 'Basic';

-- Update Corporate plan
UPDATE plans SET 
  maxKeys = 1000,
  maxFolders = 100,
  maxTeamMembers = 10,
  price = 29.00,
  hasBackup = TRUE,
  has2FA = TRUE,
  hasAPI = TRUE,
  hasAlerts = TRUE,
  hasDashboard = TRUE,
  hasAudit = FALSE
WHERE name = 'Corporate';
